<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Uplands, mesas, low hills, stabilized dunes. Soils are derived from Pleistocene sand deposits, occasionally marine siltstones overlain with a thin sand layer.  </div>
</div>

        
